    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so basically i need to watch out for these little traps that could come out of nowhere. are there any other parts of a contract that tend to have that kind of vibe? like things that seem fine on the surface but are actually kind of predatory or sneaky if you don't spot them early?",
